To incorporate the spatial aspect of the data and account for spatial correlation, a geospatial model was fitted using a spatial binomial mixed effect model. The model is of the form:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
