				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\lambda$$\end{document} takes the value between 0 and 1, and governs the degree of spatial structure present in the data. Lower values of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
